channel.title: ~ Amazon Client V6 ~ [Trytohaxme]
channel.description:
[center][size=13pt]The Official Amazon Client V6 Has Arrived! This is more of a update of v5. I haven't done a client in over one (1) whole month - Please don't critisize me to much :P[/size]
[b].:Features:.[/b]
* New Mapback * Added Themes * Connection lost and Please wait like RS * Larger Chatbox hold 8 lines! * Added Mp3 player * Added over 40 new weapons! * Added over 15 new npcs! * Added General Graador (bandos boss) * Added The correct defenders * Added Ava's Accumulater * Added Godsword Specials / server side * Added Skillcape Emotes / server side * Changed loading bar colors * Added New Skins * Perfect online and offline! * You can turn flames on and off!!! * Added custom crowns thanks to Galkons tut] * You can add models with a click of a button! * I added the interface "buy 20" * Added new npcs * Added new weapons * Perfected 7 runescape skillcape emotes * Removed Ip bar (it's like a your server kinda thing easily can be changed) * Added new vengeance skull * Flames can be turned off and on. * Fixed button position (thx Hauyser) * Fixed some item id's in class8.java * Added a folder with the latest skillcape emotes Gzipped. *thx bennyrules Wink * Fixed some other bugs/glitches * Fixed where it plays only one song lol... *thx Hauyser) * Added a add model button * Added all the blessed hides * Added a few more custom items * Added new Background * Added alot of new moster models * New Crowns * Added One Login Button/Connect * Added Server Selection (thx sir roju <3) * Two types of Batch Files Which Runs 2 different clients for example (Run BOT)-Runs from Bot.Java (Run GUI)- Runs from GUI.java * Added Full Void Knight Armour * Added all skillcapes! * Added Godsword specs ( Only works on servers that added the specs server side ) * Added Some 6 or 7 new themes * Added New Jframe * Added The Lunar tab (You need your own server) * Added The Prayer Interface (Need your own server) * Added Clear trade screen & bank! * New Background * Added a new alignment of the Jframe for Mp3 * Used the same Jframe as my Amazon Client v5 * Edited some interfaces * Added auto cache download * Background made from a friend of 4chan <3 4CHAN FTW (GO LURK NEWFAGS) :P
[b].:Pictures:.[/b]
[img]http://i37.tinypic.com/11tu53p.jpg[/img] [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/2w1w1hz.jpg[/img] [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/4jano4.jpg[/img]
[b].:Information:.[/b]
I haven't done a client in about a month or so, I'm sure you all know about my clients. I am the creator of the Amazon Client, and I think I am going to get back into Private Servers? I actually did this client out of boredom, so if you don't like then please don't complain. This is my second account Trytohaxme2, Trytohaxme was banned for evading my forums url in my signature. But I have apologized to the staff, so I will try to obtain my other account back. If you would like to know any information about this client. Feel free to contact me VIA...
1.) Private Message 2.) MSN - Explicit410@live.com (I will only add you if you post saying you are adding me)! 3.) Leave a reply on this thread.
[b].:Credits:.[/b]
Ric914 - The base Zee_Best - Lunar Interface Trytohaxme2 - The rest of the client (As far as I know).
